{"tid":2225539,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"利君雅獲逾5萬人撐 聯署斥「文革打壓異己之風死灰復燃」","createTime":"2020-10-01T11:40:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T17:31:58.000Z","uid":240362,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dbe691fe7e4932ab4e4c9c8c6883f703b4a4e976","tid":2225539,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">聯署行動連結：<a href=\"http://change.org/WeAreAllNabela\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchange.org%2FWeAreAllNabela&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w17c0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=1b7cd050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://change.org/WeAreAllNabela</a></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n港台記者利君雅遭港府以延長試用期打壓。撐公共廣播運動發起聯署聲援利君雅，短短3日已有逾5萬人參與，運動發起人羅沃啟指，政府支持者四出投訴，「似乎正令文革打壓異己之風死灰復燃」，他呼籲市民參與聯署，「向打壓新聞自由的港府說不」。<br />\n<br />\n港府藉延長利君雅試用期120日，並重啟針對她的投訴的調查來打壓。撐公共廣播聯盟運動於上月28日發起「我們都是利君雅 我們反對港府政治逼害記者」聯署，指出「政府的支持者四出投訴不同意見人士，企圖令文革打壓異己之風死灰復燃」，而港台更首當其衝，包括港台英文節目《脈搏》記者質詢世衞組織高級顧問被指不當、《頭條新聞》遭投訴至被抽起、《左右紅藍綠》更在被投訴後腰斬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/XI657HSURJCZHPFCWZ525TXBCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FXI657HSURJCZHPFCWZ525TXBCQ%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w17c0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=a2a296a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201001%2FXI657HSURJCZHPFCWZ525TXBCQ%2F&h=6a9281b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201001/XI657HSURJCZHPFCWZ525TXBCQ/</a>"},{"pid":"8bc7bbe79df78fbb563e0146e899ceddc9700256","tid":2225539,"uid":279468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:41:58.000Z","msg":"已簽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1257a06fd0c5365132f403afb515ebb38760bf84","tid":2225539,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T11:54:1